sources.title: What Price Crime?
sources.description: An undercover cop woos the sister of the crime boss in order to infiltrate the gang.

sources.title: What Price Crime (1935) CRIME THRILLER
sources.description:
Stars: Charles Starrett, Noel Madison, Virginia Cherrill 
 Director: Albert Herman

 A Federal agent is commissioned, along with several of his fellow-agents, to capture and put an end to a gang of thieves who have been systematically, using inside information, looting warehouses.

sources.title: What Price Crime (1935) Action, Adventure, Crime Full Length Movie
sources.description:
FEDERAL AGENTS WAGE WAR ON CRIME! 
Thieves break into a warehouse that stores guns, steal them and kill the night watchman. An undercover agent assigned to the case happens to get into a traffic accident with the sister of the man the police suspect is head of the burglary ring, and in order to work his way into the gang, he romances the boss' sister. 

Director: Albert Herman
Writers: Al Martin,
Stars: Charles Starrett, Noel Madison, Virginia Cherrill 
Genres: Action, Adventure, Crime, Romance, Thriller
